---
title: Slow-Cooked Chicken Cacciatore with Mash, Olives & Baby Spinach
description: It’s always nice to slow down once in a while and these slow cooked chicken is perfect for doing just that. The
chicken is baked to absorb the mouth-watering taste of the tomato, olives and thyme. Make a fluffy mash to
serve alongside it and we promise this dish will be worth the wait.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/slow-cooked-chicken-cacciatore-3c75c51d.jpg
